high_descs: Walk straight towards the sink then turn left and walk towards the oven
Look down and open the second cabinet door from the left of the oven. PIck up the glass tray inside the cabinet and close the door
Turn left then left again and walk towards the fridge
Open the fridge door and place the glass tray on the second shelf from the top. Close the fridge door, then reopen it and retrieve the tray. Close the fridge door again
Turn left and walk straight ahead. Turn right and face the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the tray in and close the microwave door
anns.task_desc: Find a glass tray in a cabinet, chill it in the fridge, then put the tray in the microwave

high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen counter to the right of the stove
Open the lower right cabinet and pick up the dish from it
Turn and walk over to the fridge
Put the dish in the fridge and take it back out
Turn left and walk over to the microwave
Put the dish into the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a dish into the microwave

high_descs: Go forward and to the left so you're standing to the left of the stove, facing thet direction.
Open the bottom right cabinet and take out the clear container.
Turn around and veer right to the fridge.
Place the container on the bottom shelf and close the door. After a moment, take the container out of the fridge.
Take a step left and look at the microwave.
Place the container in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled container in the microwave.

high_descs: Head toward the cabinet on the left, under the green cup.
Open up the cabinet on the right and take the gray container.
Move over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the container inside, close the door, wait 5 seconds, open the door and take the container back out.
Bring the container to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the container inside and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the gray container in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left and move toward the stove.
Open the bottom right cabinet and take out a bowl.
Carry the bowl and turn around and face the fridge.
Open the door and place the bowl inside. Shut the door. Open the door and take out the bowl. Shut the door.
Take a few steps to the left holding the bowl.
Place the bowl inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill and then heat a bowl.

high_descs: Look down, walk straight to the sink, turn left to face the counter with the toaster on it, walk straight to it and look down to the counter.
Open the lower cabinet, retrieve a pan inside it and close the cabinet.
Look up, turn left, walk straight, turn left to face the microwave, walk straight, turn right to face the door, walk straight and turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the pan inside, close the fridge, open the fridge, remove the pan and close the fridge.
Look up, turn left, walk straight to the sink and turn right to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the pan inside the microwave, and close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan inside the microwave.
